    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. The CFD model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under CPB conditions. RH < 1 acceptance criterion is satisfied across all 5 evaluated operating points.",
